HEADWORD: male chauvinist
<hw>male chauvinist</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A man with a belief in the
inferiority of women; one who believes in or practises male
chavinism.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> sexist.</syn>⟦br⟧
